FROM [ChatThread] AS [x.ChatThread]
LEFT JOIN [ChatHeader] AS [c.Chat] ON [x.ChatThread].[ChatId] = [c.Chat].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c.Chat.User].*
    FROM [AspNetUsers] AS [c.Chat.User]
    WHERE [c.Chat.User].[Discriminator] = N'User'
) AS [t] ON [c.Chat].[UserId] = [t].[Id]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [x0].[Id], [x0].[CreationTime]
    FROM [ChatHeader] AS [x0]
    WHERE (([x0].[IsDeleted] = 0) AND ([x0].[IsTicket] = 0)) AND (LOWER([x0].[Group]) = N'bankaccounts')
) AS [t0] ON [x.ChatThread].[ChatId] = [t0].[Id]
ORDER BY [t0].[CreationTime] DESC, [t0].[Id]" (0723d8ff)
